snippet.textDisplay: Love it!! I am totally struck by this song,  poetry, video, music, and Natasha’s powerful voice. The guitar & chorus girls have almost Pink Floyd’s feel. Very classy! Thank you everyone for singing Sir Allama Iqbal’s magnificent poetry! He would be proud of you all! In my opinion Natasha has the greatest voice ever! Love her attitude & command of the beautiful Urdu language! God bless!!!

Thank you everyone for singing Sir Allama Iqbal’s magnificent poetry! He would be proud of you all! In my opinion Natasha has the greatest voice ever! Love her attitude & command of the beautiful Urdu language! God bless!!!
